Productionization Plan

1. Hosting
•	Package script in Docker container 
•	Deploy on AWS ECS (Fargate) 
•	Store secrets in AWS Secrets Manager 
•	Basic VPC and security group setup

2. Reliability & Scaling
•	Run multiple instances for redundancy
•	Implement automatic restarts
•	Rate limit API calls (Graph, Etherscan)
•	Basic error logging and recovery

3. Monitoring
•	Deploy Grafana for visualization 

Key metrics to track: 
•	Script uptime
•	Alert frequency
•	Pool metrics (price, TVL, volume, gas price)

Multi-channel alerts: 
•	Telegram (primary)
•	Email (backup)
•	Slack (team notifications)
•	Pager Duty (on-call)
